WEBVTT

34:36.560 --> 34:37.959 line:80%
Wages will be paid daily.

34:38.600 --> 34:39.720 line:80%
That's too much.

34:39.720 --> 34:40.600 line:80%
It's not.

34:41.200 --> 34:42.470 line:80%
Generous in friendship,

34:42.470 --> 34:43.729 line:80%
exacting in business.

34:44.160 --> 34:45.140 line:80%
Tomorrow,

34:45.160 --> 34:47.689 line:80%
come over,
and I'll draw up a contract for you.
